  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Bougainville guests can enjoy breakfast on the Oasis Terrace or, for a supplement, at the Bellavista and Cavalieri Restaurants. Dinner can be taken at La Pineta and Forte Grill. You can also choose to dine in other restaurants including the Sardinian, Brazilian and Forte Grill restaurants (reservations are required). The gourmet and à la carte restaurants require reservations and a supplement is payable.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
