  <description><![CDATA[<p>Set among lush, green grounds that are filled with tropical flowers, Bouganville offers a peaceful and relaxing stay at the heart of <a data-udi="umb://document/2f4bc070df4340c5bf5b64945bcd3a5d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2f4bc070df4340c5bf5b64945bcd3a5d}" title="Forte Village Resort">Forte Village Resort</a>. Traditional style bungalows are dotted throughout the gardens and have been recently refurbished in light colours, each with an elegant patio. Its position close to the bustling piazza and a number of swimming pools and restaurants makes it perfect for both couples and families.</p>
<p>The fantastic facilities at Children’s Wonderland are within walking distance, you’ll find an aquapark here as well as fun activities for children like arts and crafts, Mario’s village – a small square with themed houses, and a theatre where younger guests can enjoy workshops.</p>]]></description>
